## SavedVariables: DingTimerDB

# HUD-first load order:
# 1. Util.lua         - shared formatting, theme, and UI helpers
# 2. Store.lua        - SavedVariables init and current schema cleanup
# 3. Core_DingTimer   - rolling XP/money state, snapshot math, and heartbeat
# 4. HUDText.lua      - pure HUD text formatting helpers
# 5. HUDGraph.lua     - HUD graph bucket math, rendering, and tooltip data
# 6. Core_HUD.lua     - floating HUD frame, animation, and visibility
# 7. Core_Events.lua  - XP and money event mutation
# 8. Actions.lua      - popup-facing setting actions and reset behavior
# 9. Commands.lua     - reduced slash command surface plus compatibility shims
# 10. UI_HUDPopup.lua - compact popup anchored to the HUD or UIParent
# 11. DingTimer.lua   - event wiring and slash command registration
Util.lua
Store.lua
Core_DingTimer.lua
HUDText.lua
HUDGraph.lua
Core_HUD.lua
Core_Events.lua
Actions.lua
Commands.lua
UI_HUDPopup.lua
